29#include "priv.h"
30#include "pad.h"
31
32static const struct nvkm_i2c_func
33nv04_i2c = {
34 .pad_x_new = nv04_i2c_pad_new,
35};
36
37int
38nv04_i2c_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_i2c **pi2c)
39{
40 return nvkm_i2c_new_(&nv04_i2c, device, index, pi2c);
41}
